{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f8d78e94db","title":"反对党的领导的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7b2451bedf","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"f8d78e94db"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"026eaa2bd0","name":"符百诚"},{"id":"5b7b8b5a0c","name":"凃安民"},{"id":"82a3f7aa1a","name":"姜纯洪"},{"id":"efce061973","name":"东北财经学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"386e3b35fb","type":"title","text":"反对党的领导的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f8d78e94db"},{"id":"0ec9bbb48e","type":"authors","text":"东北财经学院符百诚凃安民姜纯洪","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f8d78e94db"},{"id":"387a3ec8f1","type":"paragraph","text":"“我认为：领导国家的政党要通过各民主党派选举，选上哪个党，就要那个领导，民主党派也好，爱国不等于爱党。只要能把国家领导，什么党都行。”(符百诚)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f8d78e94db"},{"id":"b66dfa2a92","type":"paragraph","text":"“工人阶级既然有革命的历史必然性，何必要共产党的领导？”(凃安民)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f8d78e94db"},{"id":"a33b838158","type":"paragraph","text":"“中国没有共产党也不会亡国，你要知道中国人民是爱国的，勇敢的。”(姜纯洪)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f8d78e94db"},{"id":"7e641c2771","type":"paragraph","text":"“供销合作社有民主组织：理事会、监事会和社员代表大会，为了搞好民主管理，党、团组织必须退出合作社，有党的领导，就不能有民主管理，因为合作社的一切问题都是由党来决定。”(凃安民)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f8d78e94db"},{"id":"3bf452bd86","type":"paragraph","text":"“自然科学的发展，是不取决于党领导，而取决于人对自然研究的成果，你看资本主义国家，没有共产党的领导，科学那么发达。一百年前没有共产党就有原子能了。”(凃安民)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f8d78e94db"},{"id":"09e6fe4f6a","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《我院学生中的右派言论汇编》（中共东北财经学院委员会编，1957）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f8d78e94db"}],"page":{"id":"cacfe0d899","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f8d78e94db","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}